    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute gem! It is in truly pristine, showroom-ready condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for your next adventure, this is the one. Treat yourself to a car that\u2019s as perfect as it gets!",
      "price": 44500.0,
