      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E30 M3, a true homologation icon powered by the high-revving S14B23 dual-overhead-cam engine. This unit features impeccably balanced individual throttle bodies and original Bosch Motronic management, delivering crisp throttle response through a Getrag 265 close-ratio dogleg manual gearbox. The chassis exhibits superb torsional rigidity, complemented by a precision-tuned suspension utilizing Bilstein monotube dampers and factory-spec BBS cross-spoke alloys. Power delivery is managed via a 25% locking limited-slip differential, ensuring authentic rear-wheel-drive dynamics. From the pristine valve cover to the stainless-steel header assembly, this vehicle represents a benchmark for mechanical preservation and performance fidelity.",
